#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals.rst:211
msgid "Quantum Reservoirs"
msgstr "Reservorios CuĂˇnticos"

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals.rst:213
msgid ""
"The :class:`~qilisdk.functionals.quantum_reservoirs.QuantumReservoir` "
"functional executes a reservoir pipeline over a sequence of inputs. Each "
"layer applies an optional pre-processing circuit, an analog reservoir "
"dynamics block (:class:`~qilisdk.analog.schedule.Schedule`), and an "
"optional post-processing circuit, followed by measurements of one or more"
" observables. The optional ``qubits_to_reset`` list can be used to reset "
"selected qubits between layers."
msgstr ""
"El funcional "
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.quantum_reservoirs.QuantumReservoir` ejecuta"
" una cadena de procesamiento de reservorio sobre una secuencia de "
"entradas. Cada capa aplica un circuito de preprocesado opcional, un "
"bloque de dinĂˇmica del reservorio analĂłgico "
"(:class:`~qilisdk.analog.schedule.Schedule`), y un circuito de "
"postprocesado opcional, seguido de mediciones de uno o mĂˇs observables. "
"La lista opcional ``qubits_to_reset`` puede usarse para reiniciar cĂşbits "
"seleccionados entre capas."

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals.rst:218
msgid ""
"The reservoir inputs are represented using "
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.quantum_reservoirs.ReservoirInput` "
"parameters. These behave like standard "
":class:`~qilisdk.core.variables.Parameter` objects but are marked as non-"
"trainable so they can be driven by input data sequences rather than "
"optimization loops."
msgstr ""
"Las entradas del reservorio se representan mediante parĂˇmetros "
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.quantum_reservoirs.ReservoirInput`. Estos se"
" comportan como objetos :class:`~qilisdk.core.variables.Parameter` "
"estĂˇndar pero estĂˇn marcados como no entrenables, de modo que pueden ser "
"impulsados por secuencias de datos de entrada en lugar de bucles de "
"optimizaciĂłn."

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals.rst:224
msgid ""
"**initial_state** (:class:`~qilisdk.core.qtensor.QTensor`): Initial state"
" of the reservoir."
msgstr ""
"**initial_state** (:class:`~qilisdk.core.qtensor.QTensor`): Estado "
"inicial del reservorio."

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals.rst:225
msgid ""
"**reservoir_layer** "
"(:class:`~qilisdk.functionals.quantum_reservoirs.ReservoirLayer`): "
"Defines pre/post-processing, reservoir dynamics, observables, and reset "
"policy."
msgstr ""
"**reservoir_layer** "
"(:class:`~qilisdk.functionals.quantum_reservoirs.ReservoirLayer`): Define"
" el pre/postprocesado, la dinĂˇmica del reservorio, los observables y la "
"polĂ­tica de reinicio."

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals.rst:227
msgid ""
"**input_per_layer** (List[Dict[str, float]]): Input values to apply at "
"each layer, keyed by input parameter names (typically the labels of "
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.quantum_reservoirs.ReservoirInput`)."
msgstr ""
"**input_per_layer** (List[Dict[str, float]]): Valores de entrada a "
"aplicar en cada capa, indexados por nombres de parĂˇmetros de entrada "
"(tĂ­picamente las etiquetas de "
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.quantum_reservoirs.ReservoirInput`)."

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals.rst:232
msgid ""
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional_result.FunctionalResult`: Access "
"per-layer expectation values via :attr:`expectation_values`, plus "
"optional states via :attr:`state`."
msgstr ""
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional_result.FunctionalResult`: Acceder"
" a los valores esperados por capa mediante :attr:`expectation_values`, "
"mĂˇs los estados opcionales mediante :attr:`state`."

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals.rst:278
msgid "Encoding Input Data"
msgstr "CodificaciĂłn de Datos de Entrada"

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals.rst:280
msgid ""
"You can inject classical data into a reservoir layer in multiple places. "
"The only requirement is that the keys in ``input_per_layer`` match the "
"labels of the "
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.quantum_reservoirs.ReservoirInput` objects "
